---
---
<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    
    <div class="about-left">
      <h2 class="huge-text">Passionate about clean code & design.</h2>
      <div class="about-image-wrapper">
        <img src="/st.png" alt="Decorative tree art" class="about-image" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-right">
      <h3 class="section-heading">About Me</h3>
      <p class="bio-text">
        Hi, my name is Prem Shankar. I am an IMCA (Integrated Master of Computer Applications) student passionate about building elegant, scalable, and functional applications. I bridge the gap between design and engineering.
      </p>
      <p class="bio-text">
        I am currently looking for new opportunities to learn and grow in the tech industry, constantly exploring modern web technologies.
      </p>

      <div class="skills-container">
        <h3 class="section-heading">Core Skills</h3>
        <ul class="skills-list">
          <li>Frontend Development</li>
          <li>Backend Engineering</li>
          <li>UI / UX Principles</li>
          <li>Database Management</li>
          <li>Problem Solving</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <a href="tel:7665257565" class="contact-link">
          <span class="icon">📱</span> +91 7665257565
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 8rem 4rem;
    background-color: #000;
    color: #fff; /* Inverted colors for the About section to create contrast */
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-left {
    flex: 1;
    position: sticky;
    top: 150px;
  }

  .huge-text {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 450px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    opacity: 0.85;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));
    animation: float-simple 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float-simple {
    0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  }

  .about-right {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #ddd;
  }

  .skills-container {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .skills-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .skills-list li {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .about-left {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
